{"id": 61113, "date": "2025-10-14T04:00:25", "date_gmt": "2025-10-14T11:00:25", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=61113"}, "modified": "2026-06-12T08:08:41", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-12T15:08:41", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-october-14-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/10/14/kingdom-of-days-october-14-2/", "title": {"rendered": "October 14"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1972:\u00a0</strong>Bruce runs a classified ad in the Asbury Park Press seeking a &#8220;together and ready to travel&#8221; pianist and country violinist. Let&#8217;s hope he finds at least one of them. Maybe David Sancious is still available?</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21928\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1972-10-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1972-10-14.png?fit=1076%2C289&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1076,289\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1972-10-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1972-10-14.png?fit=758%2C204&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21928 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1972-10-14.png?resize=758%2C204&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"204\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1972-10-14.png?w=1076&amp;ssl=1 1076w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1972-10-14.png?resize=300%2C81&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1972-10-14.png?resize=1024%2C275&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1972-10-14.png?resize=768%2C206&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>At Atlantic Studios in New York City, Bruce records &#8220;Talk to Me,&#8221; &#8220;Hearts of Stone,&#8221; &#8220;City of Night,&#8221; and &#8220;Wrong Side of the Street&#8221;&#8211; all of which will go unreleased for decades&#8211;plus &#8220;The Ballad,&#8221; which is still unreleased to this day.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/rtI5TxfhhUU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1980:</strong> Bruce calls an out-of-left-field audible at his River Tour stop at Milwaukee&#8217;s Mecca Arena, resulting in his first public performance of &#8220;In the Midnight Hour.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BsPe6q9jYF0?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21849\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1980-10-14-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1980-10-14.png?fit=2073%2C1351&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2073,1351\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1980-10-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1980-10-14.png?fit=758%2C494&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21849 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1980-10-14.png?resize=758%2C494&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"494\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1980-10-14.png?w=2073&amp;ssl=1 2073w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1980-10-14.png?resize=300%2C196&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1980-10-14.png?resize=1024%2C667&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1980-10-14.png?resize=768%2C501&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1980-10-14.png?resize=1536%2C1001&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1980-10-14.png?resize=2048%2C1335&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"38547\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1980-10-14-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1980-10-14.jpg?fit=392%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"392,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1980-10-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1980-10-14.jpg?fit=392%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-38547 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1980-10-14.jpg?resize=392%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"392\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1980-10-14.jpg?w=392&amp;ssl=1 392w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/1980-10-14.jpg?resize=235%2C300&amp;ssl=1 235w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 392px) 100vw, 392px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1988:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays his first-ever show in Argentina (although half of those in attendance were from Chile) when the Human Rights Now! Tour stops in Mendoza.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21850\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1988-10-14/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1988-10-14.png?fit=2075%2C1154&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2075,1154\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1988-10-14\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1988-10-14.png?fit=758%2C421&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-21850 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1988-10-14.png?resize=758%2C422&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"422\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1988-10-14.png?w=2075&amp;ssl=1 2075w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1988-10-14.png?resize=300%2C167&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1988-10-14.png?resize=1024%2C569&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1988-10-14.png?resize=768%2C427&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1988-10-14.png?resize=1536%2C854&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1988-10-14.png?resize=2048%2C1139&amp;ssl=1 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2000:\u00a0</strong>Bruce jams with The Gotham Playboys (and future Sessions Band bandmates), who are once again the entertainment at Bruce&#8217;s belated birthday party at his house in Colts Neck.</p>\n<p><strong>2002:\u00a0</strong>The first European leg of the Rising Tour kicks off in Paris, where Elliot Murphy makes a guest appearance for &#8220;Born to Run.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Rsfjntm1jok?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0iGjKcej1Hs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wbviL1BNRag?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>The Magic Tour heads north to Canada, starting with a show at ScotiaBank Place in Ottawa, where Win Butler and Regine Chassagne of Arcade Fire guest star for the tour premiere of &#8220;State Trooper&#8221; and Bruce&#8217;s only performance of &#8220;Keep the Car Running&#8221; to date. Also tour premiering at this show: &#8220;Tougher Than the Rest&#8221; and &#8220;Backstreets,&#8221; performed back to back.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8RPriY-_iXw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IQBAuqCl9qg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"21851\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2007-10-14a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2007-10-14a.png?fit=2599%2C1187&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2599,1187\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2007-10-14a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2007-10-14a.png?fit=758%2C346&amp;ssl=1\" class