shuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2007-10-14c.png?resize=161%2C300&amp;ssl=1 161w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2007-10-14c.png?resize=549%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 549w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2007-10-14c.png?resize=768%2C1432&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/2007-10-14c.png?resize=824%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 824w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2009:\u00a0</strong>Night Two of the final four shows at the Philadelphia Spectrum opens with a rare &#8220;Thundercrack&#8221; and features the only performance to date of &#8220;What Love Can Do&#8221; along with a full album performance of\u00a0<em>Darkness on the Edge of Town</em>.</p>\n<div id=\"v-srxdgVQe-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/srxdgVQe?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-z4qotit7-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/z4qotit7?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/WVVFNDyM2as?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2017:\u00a0</strong>Bruce can&#8217;t seem to decide on the order of &#8220;Long Walk Home&#8221; and &#8220;The Rising&#8221; during his Broadway show at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City&#8211;the two songs switch places for the third time.</p>\n<p><strong>2022:\u00a0</strong>Bruce releases &#8220;Nightshift,&#8221; the second single from his upcoming album,\u00a0<em>Only the Strong Survive.</em></p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GsTKEQzLkmw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2025:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and Jeremy Allen White sit for a Q&amp;A session at Spotify Headquarters in London.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AGunhTqxHHA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparen